NB. The input for the program consists of two integers provided on a single line, separated by a space. The output should be the sum of these integers.
NB.
NB. Input
NB. Two integers on a single line.
NB.
NB. Output
NB. The sum of the two integers.
NB.
NB. Examples
NB. Input #1
NB. 12 9
NB.
NB. Answer #1
NB. 21

1!:2&2 (12 + 9)
